high_descs: turn right, head to the door, turn right, heads to the shelf, turn right, head to the stove, turn right to face the table
take the tomato in front of the fork
turn left, advance next to the stove and not next to the table, turn right, head to the refrigerator, turn left, head to sink
put tomato in sink on right side
take knife from sink
use knife from sink to make a tomato slice
put knife in sink
take tomato slice from sink
put tomato slice on left side of sink, use water from faucet to cover items in sink with water, take the tomato slice from the left side of the sink
turn right to face microwave
put tomato slice in microwave
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed slice of tomato in the microwave

high_descs: Turn right, move to the corner with the brown shelving unit, turn right again and stop between the window and counter, facing the tomatoes.
Pick up the tomato closest to you from the counter.
Carry the tomato to the kitchen sink.
Place the tomato in the kitchen sink.
Pick up the knife from the kitchen sink.
Slice the top off the tomato in the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Pick up the slice you just cut from the tomato in the sink.
Place the slice of tomato in the sink, turn the water on, and wash it.
Remove the freshly washed tomato slice from the sink.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed tomato slice in the microwave.

high_descs: turn right, walk towards the door, turn right at the door, then turn right at the shelf, stop at the kitchen island
Pick up the the tomato from the island
walk towards the sink next to the refrigerator
put the tomato in the sink
retrieve a knife  from the sink
cut the tomato in the sink
put the knife back in the sink
wash the tomato in the sink
take the tomato out of the sink
turn right and walk towards the microwave
put the tomato in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Cook a sliced tomato in the microwave
